DEPOT

An IMAP server in Java.

    Issues and Tasks: http://blogometer.com/trac/incubator
    Source: http://github.com/bigeasy/depot/tree/master
    Contact: alan@blogometer.com

PURPOSE

Depot is an IMAP server that pipes its messages through Java mail filters. It is
a framework for creating mail applications in Java.

MOTIVATION

Could not find a lightweight Java implementation of the mail protocols.
